      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely slice your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>leek[s]</strong> in half lengthways, then wash to remove any grit from between the leaves and top, tail and slice finely</p><p>Top, tail, peel and cut your <strong>carrot[s]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>in half lengthways, then slice finely</p><p>Deseed your <strong>pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1637828604257-x200.jpg",
