        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is lightly coloured, add your <strong>cornflour</strong> to the pot with the <strong>chopped shallot</strong>, <strong>sliced leek</strong>, <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>carrot</strong> and <strong>pepper strips</strong></p><p>Stir everything together and cook for 1-2 min or until the shallot has slightly softened</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1637828609778-x200.jpg",
