        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>creamed</strong> <strong>coconut</strong> roughly (if required!)</p><p>Dissolve your <strong>chopped creamed coconut</strong> in 700ml <span class=\"text-purple\"><span class=\"text-danger\">[910ml]</span> [1.2 L]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> with your <strong>lime leaf[ves]</strong> and <strong>fish sauce</strong> – this is your <strong>coconut stock</strong></p>",
