      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the shallot has slightly softened, add the <strong>coconut stock </strong>to the pot<strong> </strong>with a grind of <strong>black</strong> <strong>pepper </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, lower the heat to medium-low and cook, covered, for 25 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) and the potatoes are tender – this is your <strong>Thai-style spiced chicken thigh, leek & potato soup</strong></p>",
