    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the soup is ready, remove the <strong>lime leaf[ves]</strong> and stir through the <strong>chopped coriander</strong></p><p>Taste for seasoning, adding more <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> if needed</p>",
